{
  "texts": [
    "It has been observed that he skips therapy appointments.",
    "The wife is concerned because he shows no interest in her visits.",
    "When asked, he states that he sees no point in further treatment because he has little hope that his condition will improve.",
    "However, none of that really matters anymore.",
    "He is also not afraid of another heart attack; on the contrary, then his misery would come to an end."
  ]
}